I'm willing to make a site for the IRL stuff if enough people will 
participate. I think its a good idea. I have a pic or two I might be able to 
contribute.

Also, since Crow Lord let me borrow his Maximal and Alliance chars when he 
left on vacation, I'm going to use them now.

::Rhinox::

Rhinox walks out of the Ark, looking at the Newcomers and their crate. He was 
surprised, he didn't think they would honor the deal.

"You can leave it right here," he says to them, his hand near his gun, "We'll 
put it in our storage."
